oard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=225.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=95%><tr><td bgcolor=#000000><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Author</font></td><td valign=top bgcolor=#cc9966 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uariahceleneevanda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ariah Celene Evanda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#993300>(4/4/02 11:48:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Visiting and Questioning</span><hr size=1> Ariah rode up on the horse she was given for winter solstice. There was a slight smile on her face, though it was apparent something troubled her. She nodded to whatever guards were around and tied up her horse in the stables before moving towards Alysia's hut. Ari looked different than she had before, though it wasn't yet apparent why. There was just a different air around her now, a different vibe, if you will. A light knock was given to Alysia's door and Ari folded her arms across her chest to wait for an answer. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 331<br> <font color=#993300>(4/5/02 3:59:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ariah</span><hr size=1> Alysia's door opened lightly as the young amazon Queen looked out. Her green eyes blinked as she saw her friend and smiled.<br><br>&quot;Ariah? What brings you here?&quot;<br><br>She saw the trouble in her athelfi's eyes. . . . what could it possibly be. So much had been happening as of lately. With everything happening in XVH, and her memories returning, and then this new battle with Hell . . . she didn't know what else was going to happen. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uariahceleneevanda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ariah Celene Evanda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/7/02 1:11:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hope?</span><hr size=1> She smiled lightly and nodded to her.<br><br>&quot;Greetings. I know I have horrible timing, what with you just starting to get your memories back and with everything else, but I have an urgent question and you're the only one I could think of to answer it. There have been rumors reaching Ephesus, Alysia, of Hope. They say she is up to no good agian. Do you know if this is true? She is a member of my tribe, you see, and well... I obviously cannot have her in my tribe if there is any truth in the rumors. Have you heard anything?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 333<br> <font color=#993300>(4/7/02 2:03:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hope</span><hr size=1> Alysia's eyes instantly lit up with a glare.<br><br>&quot;Ariah, listen to me. I have inside information that Hope may be using the Amazons to assist in Lucifers take on evil. I'm not sure how, but she wants our lands. They have already made an attack on my wolves.&quot;<br><br>Alysia was serious about this. One woman could pose such a threat. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uariahceleneevanda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ariah Celene Evanda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(4/7/02 2:58:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hope</span><hr size=1> She blinked a moment and then nodded again.<br><br>&quot;Thank you. Lucifer, yes... well I believe she's had ties with him in the past, though I was led to believe that these were all in the past. Apparently, though, I was led astray. Are your wolves alright? No injuries came out of her actions, I hope. She will be suspended from ALtA until I can get a confirmation.&quot;<br><br>She thought silently for a moment while she waited for anything else Aly had to say. It came to mind that perhaps her advisor, Genesis, would be a most valuable person to talk to right now, since she had dealt with both Hope and Lucifer many times and seemed to be the most informed one thigns that were going on pertaining to them. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uariahceleneevanda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ariah Celene Evanda</A> at: 4/7/02 3:00:22 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 334<br> <font color=#993300>(4/8/02 2:09:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .....</span><hr size=1> Alysia looked down as a small framed wolf came to the door. She smiled and scratched his ear for him.<br><br>&quot;The wolves are fine, yes.&quot;<br><br>She then looked in Ariah's eyes and paused as she could almost hear her thoughts.<br><br>&quot;Speaking with Genesis will do no good. She has no recollection of her times with Lucifer. And the only things she remembers about Hope are back when Kimbia was killed.&quot;<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=225.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=225.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=225.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=225.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=225.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive em